flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> SelectLift[Select Lift Type]
    SelectLift --> InputMethod{Choose Input<br/>Method?}

    InputMethod -- "Live Recording" --> StartCam[Start Camera<br/>and Record Lift]
    StartCam --> Capture[Capture Video<br/>Using Webcam]
    Capture --> StopRec[Stop Recording<br/>and Submit]
    StopRec --> SendRec[Send Recorded<br/>Video to Server]
    SendRec --> Process[Process and<br/>Prepare Video]

    InputMethod -- "Upload Video" --> Upload[Upload Video<br/>From Device]
    Upload --> Submit[Submit File<br/>to Server]

    Process --> Extract[Extract Frames<br/>From Video]
    Submit --> Extract

    Extract --> Pose[Detect Body Pose<br/>in Each Frame]
    Pose --> Filter{Is Pose<br/>Detected?}

    Filter -- "No" --> LowConf[Low Confidence<br/>Warning]
    LowConf -.-> Pose

    Filter -- "Yes" --> Angles[Calculate Body<br/>Angles]
    Angles --> Phases[Identify Lift<br/>Phases]
    Phases --> BarPath[Track Barbell<br/>Movement Path]
    BarPath --> Faults[Evaluate Lifting<br/>Form]
    Faults --> Annotate[Create Annotated<br/>Video with Overlay]

    Annotate --> PrintStats[Record Session<br/>Results]
    Annotate --> SaveVid[Save Annotated<br/>Video]

    SaveVid --> UploadR2[Upload Video<br/>to Cloud Storage]
    UploadR2 --> UpdateResults

    PrintStats --> UpdateResults[Display Analysis<br/>Results and Feedback]

    UpdateResults --> SaveHistory{Save to<br/>Gallery?}

    SaveHistory -- "No" --> Finish([End])

    SaveHistory -- "Yes" --> SaveTitle[Enter Gallery<br/>Title]
    SaveTitle --> AddDB[Save Record<br/>to Database]
    AddDB --> Confirm[Show Success<br/>Confirmation]
    Confirm --> Finish

    %% Styling - Dark theme matching reference image
    %% Start/End nodes - Pink/Coral
    style Start fill:#F8B4C8,stroke:#E091A8,stroke-width:2px,color:#1E1E3F
    style Finish fill:#F8B4C8,stroke:#E091A8,stroke-width:2px,color:#1E1E3F

    %% Decision diamonds - Orange/Peach
    style InputMethod fill:#E8A87C,stroke:#D4956A,stroke-width:2px,color:#1E1E3F
    style Filter fill:#E8A87C,stroke:#D4956A,stroke-width:2px,color:#1E1E3F
    style SaveHistory fill:#E8A87C,stroke:#D4956A,stroke-width:2px,color:#1E1E3F

